product.bullet_points:
• 【Composite Iron Base】Designed with the aim of durability and stability, the floor TV stand's metal base is cast using three layers of composite materials, which brings you peace of mind and the safety of your TV. Now you can use this high-quality 65-inch TV stand to support a TV weighing up to 88 pounds
• 【Unparalleled Compatibility】Not only high compatibility with various TVs, universal TV stand for 32-65 inch TVs, it means our FITUEYES floor TV stand is compatible with 32, 37, 42, 46, 50, 55, and 65-inch LCD, LED, OLED, Plasma, flat panel, or curved screen TVs. But also suitable for use in your home, living room, bedroom, office, meeting room, and etc. Please ensure your TV's VESA mounting holes are between 100x100 and 400x400 mm.
• 【Unbeatable Viewing Experience】The 65-inch floor TV stand is designed with 8 height adjustment modes and a 30-degree rotation adjustment function on both sides. Now you can adjust the height between 47.8" and 56.1" of your TV, satisfying your various viewing needs and providing an unparalleled viewing experience!
• 【Comfortable and Convenient User Experience】For your comfortable user experience, the Universal Swivel TV Stand is designed with clean and efficient cable management and safety locks. This white tall TV stand can easily collect messy cables, which brings you comfort and tranquility. In addition, the sturdy safety lock on the portable TV stand will firmly protect your TV.
• 【User-Friendly Installation】There’s no need to drill your beautiful wall, and the TV stand mount for the living room is easy to put together by following the installation manual. FITUEYES TV floor stand will provide necessary tools and hardware to get your portable TV stand, and instructions are pretty straightforward.
